snippet: Ravindra Jadeja ripped the heart out of England's batting order to bowl India to a thumping innings and 75-run victory in the fifth and final test on Tuesday....
lead_paragraph: Ravindra Jadeja ripped the heart out of England's batting order to bowl India to a thumping innings and 75-run victory in the fifth and final test on Tuesday.

headline.main: Jadeja Spins India to Crushing Win Over England
headline.print_headline: Jadeja Spins India to Crushing Win Over England
